25|$|<b>Aquifer</b> <b>storage</b> and {{recovery}} (ASR) (also {{referred to as}} Managed Aquifer Recharge) aims to enhance water recharge to underground aquifers through gravity feed or pumping. It can be an alternative to large surface storages with water being pumped up again from below the surface in dry periods.|$|E
