40|$|This is a {{fundamental}} study of trapping of non-wetting fluids in porous media. When injecting CO~ 2 ~ into an <b>aquifer</b> for carbon <b>storage,</b> the non-wetting phase (CO~ 2 ~) is trapped due to capillary forces. This process is investigated in the laboratory for analogue fluids. |$|R
